message:
Hi Michael! I hope you’re having a wonderful day! Thank you very much, I really appreciate that you think it’s beautiful and shared your story with me.

That’s awesome you tried to make a watch! I’m asked pretty frequently if I make watches since I make jewelry but I wouldn’t even know where to start to be honest. I admire you attempted to make one! It’s a true art. You should give it another go!

Hi! Your jewelry is beautiful. I attempted to make a watch once. I bought an old tanner movement and cnc’d the lugs and case but got frustrated moving the crown 90 degrees and abandoned the project. I still have the parts. Rambling a bit but I appreciate what you do.
